[
  {
    "text": "My mother was a philanthropist.",
    "start": 13.04,
    "duration": 2.52
  },
  {
    "text": "And now I know you're asking --",
    "start": 17.0,
    "duration": 2.176
  },
  {
    "text": "let me give you the answer:\nyes, a little bit like Melinda Gates --",
    "start": 19.2,
    "duration": 3.536
  },
  {
    "text": "(Laughter)",
    "start": 22.76,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "but with a lot less money.",
    "start": 24.0,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "(Laughter)",
    "start": 25.96,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "She carried out her philanthropy\nin our community",
    "start": 28.16,
    "duration": 4.616
  },
  {
    "text": "through a practice we call, \"isirika.\"",
    "start": 32.8,
    "duration": 2.6
  },
  {
    "text": "She supported the education\nof scores of children",
    "start": 36.2,
    "duration": 5.016
  },
  {
    "text": "and invited many\nto live with us in our home",
    "start": 41.24,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "in order to access schools.",
    "start": 44.2,
    "duration": 1.56
  },
  {
    "text": "She mobilized resources\nfor building the local health clinic",
    "start": 46.76,
    "duration": 3.96
  },
  {
    "text": "and the maternity wing\nis named in memory of her.",
    "start": 51.8,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "But most important,",
    "start": 57.36,
    "duration": 2.216
  },
  {
    "text": "she was endeared by the community\nfor her organizing skills,",
    "start": 59.6,
    "duration": 5.16
  },
  {
    "text": "because she organized the community,",
    "start": 65.56,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "and specifically women,",
    "start": 68.08,
    "duration": 2.096
  },
  {
    "text": "to find solutions",
    "start": 70.2,
    "duration": 2.096
  },
  {
    "text": "to anything that was needed.",
    "start": 72.32,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "She did all of this through isirika.",
    "start": 75.2,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me repeat that word for you again:",
    "start": 79.24,
    "duration": 2.416
  },
  {
    "text": "isirika.",
    "start": 81.68,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "Now it's your turn. Say it with me.",
    "start": 82.92,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "(Audience) Isirika.",
    "start": 84.8,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "Musimbi Kanyoro: Thank you.",
    "start": 86.16,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "That word is in my language, Maragoli,",
    "start": 87.68,
    "duration": 3.176
  },
  {
    "text": "spoken in western Kenya,",
    "start": 90.88,
    "duration": 1.776
  },
  {
    "text": "and now you speak my language.",
    "start": 92.68,
    "duration": 1.776
  },
  {
    "text": "(Laughter)",
    "start": 94.48,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "So, isirika is a pragmatic way of life",
    "start": 95.84,
    "duration": 5.176
  },
  {
    "text": "that embraces charity,",
    "start": 101.04,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "services",
    "start": 104.0,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "and philanthropy all together.",
    "start": 105.28,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "The essence of isirika",
    "start": 109.28,
    "duration": 1.96
  },
  {
    "text": "is to make it clear to everybody",
    "start": 112.84,
    "duration": 3.576
  },
  {
    "text": "that you're your sister's keeper --",
    "start": 116.44,
    "duration": 2.176
  },
  {
    "text": "and yes,",
    "start": 118.64,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "you're your brother's keeper.",
    "start": 119.96,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Mutual responsibility\nfor caring for one another.",
    "start": 123.04,
    "duration": 4.76
  },
  {
    "text": "A literal, simple English translation\nwould be equal generosity,",
    "start": 129.0,
    "duration": 5.856
  },
  {
    "text": "but the deep philosophical meaning",
    "start": 134.88,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "is caring, together, for one another.",
    "start": 137.4,
    "duration": 4.6
  },
  {
    "text": "So how does isirika really happen?",
    "start": 142.84,
    "duration": 2.0
  },
  {
    "text": "I grew up in a farming community",
    "start": 146.44,
    "duration": 4.696
  },
  {
    "text": "in western Kenya.",
    "start": 151.16,
    "duration": 1.4
  },
  {
    "text": "I remember vividly the many times",
    "start": 154.04,
    "duration": 3.416
  },
  {
    "text": "that neighbors would go\nto a neighbor's home --",
    "start": 157.48,
    "duration": 3.296
  },
  {
    "text": "a sick neighbor's home --",
    "start": 160.8,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "and harvest their crop for them.",
    "start": 162.4,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "I tagged alongside with my mother\nto community events",
    "start": 165.52,
    "duration": 4.536
  },
  {
    "text": "and to women's events,",
    "start": 170.08,
    "duration": 1.976
  },
  {
    "text": "and had the conversation\nabout vaccinations in school,",
    "start": 172.08,
    "duration": 4.976
  },
  {
    "text": "building the health center",
    "start": 177.08,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "and really big things --",
    "start": 178.84,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "renewing seeds for the next\nplanting season.",
    "start": 180.12,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "And often, the community\nwould come together",
    "start": 184.8,
    "duration": 3.096
  },
  {
    "text": "to contribute money\nto send a neighbor's child to school --",
    "start": 187.92,
    "duration": 4.216
  },
  {
    "text": "not only in the country",
    "start": 192.16,
    "duration": 3.096
  },
  {
    "text": "but to universities abroad as well.",
    "start": 195.28,
    "duration": 2.4
  },
  {
    "text": "And so we have a surgeon.",
    "start": 198.24,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "The first surgeon in my country\ncame from that rural village.",
    "start": 200.72,
    "duration": 3.896
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 204.64,
    "duration": 4.056
  },
  {
    "text": "So ...",
    "start": 208.72,
    "duration": 1.696
  },
  {
    "text": "what isirika did was to be inclusive.",
    "start": 210.44,
    "duration": 3.856
  },
  {
    "text": "We as children would stand\nalongside the adults",
    "start": 214.32,
    "duration": 4.056
  },
  {
    "text": "and give our contributions of money,",
    "start": 218.4,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "and our names were inscripted\nin the community book",
    "start": 220.76,
    "duration": 3.416
  },
  {
    "text": "just like every adult.",
    "start": 224.2,
    "duration": 2.12
  },
  {
    "text": "And then I grew up,",
    "start": 227.52,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "went to universities\nback at home and abroad,",
    "start": 229.16,
    "duration": 4.216
  },
  {
    "text": "obtained a few degrees here and there,",
    "start": 233.4,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "became organized",
    "start": 236.36,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "and took up international jobs,",
    "start": 238.2,
    "duration": 3.216
  },
  {
    "text": "working in development,",
    "start": 241.44,
    "duration": 2.096
  },
  {
    "text": "humanitarian work",
    "start": 243.56,
    "duration": 1.896
  },
  {
    "text": "and philanthropy.",
    "start": 245.48,
    "duration": 1.24
  },
  {
    "text": "And very soon,",
    "start": 247.68,
    "duration": 1.44
  },
  {
    "text": "isirika began to become small.",
    "start": 250.24,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "It dissipated",
    "start": 254.16,
    "duration": 1.376
  },
  {
    "text": "and then just disappeared.",
    "start": 255.56,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "In each place,",
    "start": 258.0,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "I gained a new vocabulary.",
    "start": 259.36,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "The vocabulary of donors and recipients.",
    "start": 261.32,
    "duration": 3.44
  },
  {
    "text": "The vocabulary of measuring impact,",
    "start": 265.96,
    "duration": 4.496
  },
  {
    "text": "return on investment ...",
    "start": 270.48,
    "duration": 1.84
  },
  {
    "text": "projects and programs.",
    "start": 273.56,
    "duration": 1.8
  },
  {
    "text": "Communities such as my childhood community",
    "start": 276.8,
    "duration": 2.776
  },
  {
    "text": "became referred to\nas \"poor, vulnerable populations.\"",
    "start": 279.6,
    "duration": 4.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Those are the communities\nof which literature speaks about",
    "start": 285.2,
    "duration": 3.816
  },
  {
    "text": "as living on less than a dollar a day,",
    "start": 289.04,
    "duration": 3.936
  },
  {
    "text": "and they become the targets\nfor poverty eradication programs.",
    "start": 293.0,
    "duration": 4.176
  },
  {
    "text": "And by the way,",
    "start": 297.2,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "they are the targets of our first",
    "start": 298.52,
    "duration": 2.656
  },
  {
    "text": "United Nations'\nsustainable development goal.",
    "start": 301.2,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, I'm really interested",
    "start": 307.32,
    "duration": 3.456
  },
  {
    "text": "that we find solutions to poverty",
    "start": 310.8,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "and to the world's other many big problems",
    "start": 313.32,
    "duration": 2.736
  },
  {
    "text": "because they do exist.",
    "start": 316.08,
    "duration": 1.36
  },
  {
    "text": "I however think\nthat we could do a better job,",
    "start": 318.76,
    "duration": 3.456
  },
  {
    "text": "and we could do a better job\nby embracing isirika.",
    "start": 322.24,
    "duration": 4.216
  },
  {
    "text": "So let me tell you how.",
    "start": 326.48,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "First, isirika affirms common humanity.",
    "start": 328.88,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "For whatever that you do,",
    "start": 333.08,
    "duration": 2.216
  },
  {
    "text": "you begin from the premise\nthat you're human together.",
    "start": 335.32,
    "duration": 3.56
  },
  {
    "text": "When you begin that you're human together,",
    "start": 340.36,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "you see each other differently.",
    "start": 342.92,
    "duration": 2.32
  },
  {
    "text": "You don't see a refugee first",
    "start": 345.92,
    "duration": 2.856
  },
  {
    "text": "and you don't see a woman first",
    "start": 348.8,
    "duration": 2.616
  },
  {
    "text": "and you don't see\na person with disability first.",
    "start": 351.44,
    "duration": 3.216
  },
  {
    "text": "You see a human being first.",
    "start": 354.68,
    "duration": 2.896
  },
  {
    "text": "That is the essence\nof seeing a person first.",
    "start": 357.6,
    "duration": 3.296
  },
  {
    "text": "And when you do that,",
    "start": 360.92,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "you value their ideas,",
    "start": 362.8,
    "duration": 2.216
  },
  {
    "text": "you value their contribution --",
    "start": 365.04,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "small or big.",
    "start": 366.92,
    "duration": 1.48
  },
  {
    "text": "And you value what\nthey bring to the table.",
    "start": 369.04,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "That is the essence of isirika.",
    "start": 372.8,
    "duration": 2.04
  },
  {
    "text": "I just want to imagine\nwhat it would look like",
    "start": 377.4,
    "duration": 3.616
  },
  {
    "text": "if everyone in this room --",
    "start": 381.04,
    "duration": 2.856
  },
  {
    "text": "a medical doctor, a parent,",
    "start": 383.92,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "a lawyer, a philanthropist,",
    "start": 385.88,
    "duration": 1.72
  },
  {
    "text": "whatever you are --",
    "start": 388.96,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "if you embraced isirika",
    "start": 390.52,
    "duration": 3.096
  },
  {
    "text": "and made it your default.",
    "start": 393.64,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "What could we achieve for each other?",
    "start": 396.28,
    "duration": 2.936
  },
  {
    "text": "What could we achieve for humanity?",
    "start": 399.24,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "What could we achieve for peace issues?",
    "start": 402.72,
    "duration": 3.336
  },
  {
    "text": "What could we achieve for medical science?",
    "start": 406.08,
    "duration": 4.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Let me give you a couple of hints,",
    "start": 411.24,
    "duration": 2.056
  },
  {
    "text": "because I'm going to ask you\nto accompany me",
    "start": 413.32,
    "duration": 3.696
  },
  {
    "text": "in this process of rebuilding\nand reclaiming isirika with me.",
    "start": 417.04,
    "duration": 5.8
  },
  {
    "text": "First, you have to have faith",
    "start": 424.08,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "that we are one humanity,",
    "start": 428.16,
    "duration": 2.176
  },
  {
    "text": "we have one planet",
    "start": 430.36,
    "duration": 2.016
  },
  {
    "text": "and we don't have two choices about that.",
    "start": 432.4,
    "duration": 2.256
  },
  {
    "text": "So there's not going to be a wall\nthat is high enough",
    "start": 434.68,
    "duration": 3.656
  },
  {
    "text": "to separate humanity.",
    "start": 438.36,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "So give up the walls.",
    "start": 439.96,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "Give them up.",
    "start": 441.8,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 443.08,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "And we don't have a planet B to go to.",
    "start": 444.84,
    "duration": 3.376
  },
  {
    "text": "So that's really important.",
    "start": 448.24,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "Make that clear;",
    "start": 450.0,
    "duration": 1.416
  },
  {
    "text": "move onto the next stage.",
    "start": 451.44,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "The second stage: remember,",
    "start": 453.0,
    "duration": 2.16
  },
  {
    "text": "in isirika, every idea counts.",
    "start": 456.68,
    "duration": 2.48
  },
  {
    "text": "Bridges have big posters",
    "start": 460.56,
    "duration": 2.416
  },
  {
    "text": "and they have nails.",
    "start": 463.0,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": "Every idea counts --",
    "start": 466.56,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "small or big counts.",
    "start": 468.04,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "And third,",
    "start": 471.28,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "isirika affirms",
    "start": 472.76,
    "duration": 1.296
  },
  {
    "text": "that those who have more\nreally enjoy the privilege of giving more.",
    "start": 474.08,
    "duration": 5.08
  },
  {
    "text": "It is a privilege to give more.",
    "start": 479.88,
    "duration": 2.096
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 482.0,
    "duration": 2.176
  },
  {
    "text": "And this is the time\nfor women to give more for women.",
    "start": 484.2,
    "duration": 5.656
  },
  {
    "text": "It is the time to give more for women.",
    "start": 489.88,
    "duration": 2.44
  },
  {
    "text": "Our parents, when they brought in\nother children to live with us,",
    "start": 493.52,
    "duration": 4.776
  },
  {
    "text": "they didn't ask our permission.",
    "start": 498.32,
    "duration": 1.88
  },
  {
    "text": "They made it clear\nthat they had a responsibility",
    "start": 501.0,
    "duration": 3.256
  },
  {
    "text": "because they had gone to school",
    "start": 504.28,
    "duration": 2.416
  },
  {
    "text": "and they had an earning.",
    "start": 506.72,
    "duration": 1.64
  },
  {
    "text": "And they made it clear\nthat we should understand",
    "start": 509.08,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "that their prosperity\nwas not our entitlement,",
    "start": 511.64,
    "duration": 4.856
  },
  {
    "text": "and I think that's good\nwisdom from isirika.",
    "start": 516.52,
    "duration": 2.776
  },
  {
    "text": "We could use that wisdom today,\nI think, in every culture,",
    "start": 519.32,
    "duration": 3.976
  },
  {
    "text": "in every place,",
    "start": 523.32,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "passing to the next generation\nwhat we could do together.",
    "start": 525.88,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": "I have,",
    "start": 531.64,
    "duration": 1.895
  },
  {
    "text": "over the years,",
    "start": 533.559,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "encountered isirika in many places,",
    "start": 535.159,
    "duration": 2.921
  },
  {
    "text": "but what gives me really the passion today",
    "start": 539.12,
    "duration": 3.456
  },
  {
    "text": "to embrace isirika",
    "start": 542.6,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "is the work that I do\nwith women all over the world",
    "start": 544.44,
    "duration": 3.296
  },
  {
    "text": "through the Global Fund for Women,",
    "start": 547.76,
    "duration": 2.256
  },
  {
    "text": "though women's funds",
    "start": 550.04,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "and through women's movements globally.",
    "start": 551.52,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "If you work with women,",
    "start": 554.92,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "you change every day",
    "start": 556.48,
    "duration": 2.176
  },
  {
    "text": "because you experience them living\nisirika together in what they do.",
    "start": 558.68,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "In the work that I do,",
    "start": 565.16,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "we trust women leaders and their ideas.",
    "start": 566.44,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "And we support them with funding\nso that they can expand,",
    "start": 571.36,
    "duration": 4.696
  },
  {
    "text": "they can grow",
    "start": 576.08,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "and they can thrive\nwithin their own communities.",
    "start": 577.6,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "A woman in 1990 came\nto the Global Fund with a big idea --",
    "start": 582.44,
    "duration": 5.296
  },
  {
    "text": "a woman from Mexico\nby the name of Lucero González.",
    "start": 587.76,
    "duration": 3.856
  },
  {
    "text": "She wanted to begin a fund\nthat would support a movement",
    "start": 591.64,
    "duration": 4.936
  },
  {
    "text": "that would be rooted\nin the communities in Mexico.",
    "start": 596.6,
    "duration": 2.896
  },
  {
    "text": "And she received a grant\nof 7,500 US dollars.",
    "start": 599.52,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, 25 years later,",
    "start": 606.64,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "Semillas, the name of the fund,",
    "start": 610.2,
    "duration": 2.816
  },
  {
    "text": "has raised and spent,",
    "start": 613.04,
    "duration": 2.336
  },
  {
    "text": "within the community,",
    "start": 615.4,
    "duration": 1.616
  },
  {
    "text": "17.8 million dollars.",
    "start": 617.04,
    "duration": 3.536
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 620.6,
    "duration": 2.816
  },
  {
    "text": "They have impacted\nover two million people,",
    "start": 623.44,
    "duration": 6.816
  },
  {
    "text": "and they work with a group\nof 600,000 women in Mexico.",
    "start": 630.28,
    "duration": 5.8
  },
  {
    "text": "During the recent earthquake,",
    "start": 636.76,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "they were so well rooted",
    "start": 641.16,
    "duration": 1.936
  },
  {
    "text": "that they could quickly assess\nwithin the community and with others,",
    "start": 643.12,
    "duration": 4.856
  },
  {
    "text": "what were the short-term needs\nand what were the long-term needs.",
    "start": 648.0,
    "duration": 4.536
  },
  {
    "text": "And I tell you,",
    "start": 652.56,
    "duration": 1.576
  },
  {
    "text": "long after the lights\nhave gone off Mexico,",
    "start": 654.16,
    "duration": 3.736
  },
  {
    "text": "Semillas will be there",
    "start": 657.92,
    "duration": 2.456
  },
  {
    "text": "with the communities, with the women,",
    "start": 660.4,
    "duration": 2.496
  },
  {
    "text": "for a very long time.",
    "start": 662.92,
    "duration": 1.976
  },
  {
    "text": "And that's what I'm talking about:",
    "start": 664.92,
    "duration": 2.376
  },
  {
    "text": "when we are able to support\nthe ideas of communities",
    "start": 667.32,
    "duration": 4.576
  },
  {
    "text": "that are rooted within their own setting.",
    "start": 671.92,
    "duration": 3.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Thirty years ago,",
    "start": 675.76,
    "duration": 1.2
  },
  {
    "text": "there was very little funding\nthat went directly to women's hands",
    "start": 678.52,
    "duration": 4.776
  },
  {
    "text": "in their communities.",
    "start": 683.32,
    "duration": 1.52
  },
  {
    "text": "Today we celebrate 168 women's funds",
    "start": 685.4,
    "duration": 6.176
  },
  {
    "text": "all over the world,",
    "start": 691.6,
    "duration": 1.336
  },
  {
    "text": "100 of which are in this country.",
    "start": 692.96,
    "duration": 2.64
  },
  {
    "text": "And they support --",
    "start": 696.68,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 698.16,
    "duration": 1.656
  },
  {
    "text": "they support grassroots\nwomen's organizations --",
    "start": 699.84,
    "duration": 2.96
  },
  {
    "text": "community organizations\nunder the leadership of girls and women,",
    "start": 704.08,
    "duration": 5.176
  },
  {
    "text": "and together we have been able,",
    "start": 709.28,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "collectively,",
    "start": 711.84,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "to give a billion dollars\nto women and girls-led organizations.",
    "start": 713.08,
    "duration": 5.616
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 718.72,
    "duration": 5.136
  },
  {
    "text": "But the challenge begins today.",
    "start": 723.88,
    "duration": 3.24
  },
  {
    "text": "The challenge begins today",
    "start": 727.84,
    "duration": 1.776
  },
  {
    "text": "because we see women everywhere\norganizing as isirika,",
    "start": 729.64,
    "duration": 5.496
  },
  {
    "text": "including women\norganizing as isirika in TED.",
    "start": 735.16,
    "duration": 4.68
  },
  {
    "text": "Because isirika is the evergreen wisdom\nthat lives in communities.",
    "start": 740.44,
    "duration": 4.28
  },
  {
    "text": "You find it in indigenous communities,",
    "start": 746.48,
    "duration": 2.776
  },
  {
    "text": "in rural communities.",
    "start": 749.28,
    "duration": 1.6
  },
  {
    "text": "And what it really ingrains in people",
    "start": 751.68,
    "duration": 4.296
  },
  {
    "text": "is that ability to trust",
    "start": 756.0,
    "duration": 3.016
  },
  {
    "text": "and to move the agenda ahead.",
    "start": 759.04,
    "duration": 3.36
  },
  {
    "text": "So, three things that I have learned\nthat I want to share with you",
    "start": 763.04,
    "duration": 3.816
  },
  {
    "text": "through my work.",
    "start": 766.88,
    "duration": 1.496
  },
  {
    "text": "One: if you want to solve\nthe world's biggest problems,",
    "start": 768.4,
    "duration": 6.256
  },
  {
    "text": "invest in women and girls.",
    "start": 774.68,
    "duration": 3.216
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 777.92,
    "duration": 5.296
  },
  {
    "text": "Not only do they expand the investment,",
    "start": 783.24,
    "duration": 3.016
  },
  {
    "text": "but they care for everyone\nin the community.",
    "start": 786.28,
    "duration": 2.376
  },
  {
    "text": "Not only their needs\nbut the needs of their children,",
    "start": 788.68,
    "duration": 3.896
  },
  {
    "text": "the needs of the rest of the community,",
    "start": 792.6,
    "duration": 2.056
  },
  {
    "text": "the needs of the elderly,",
    "start": 794.68,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "and most important,",
    "start": 796.56,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "they protect themselves --",
    "start": 798.32,
    "duration": 2.776
  },
  {
    "text": "which is really important --",
    "start": 801.12,
    "duration": 1.856
  },
  {
    "text": "and they protect their communities.",
    "start": 803.0,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "Women who know how to protect themselves",
    "start": 806.36,
    "duration": 2.616
  },
  {
    "text": "know what it means to make a difference.",
    "start": 809.0,
    "duration": 2.72
  },
  {
    "text": "And the second reason that I'm asking\nyou to invest in women and girls",
    "start": 812.36,
    "duration": 3.896
  },
  {
    "text": "is because this is the smartest\nthing you could ever do",
    "start": 816.28,
    "duration": 4.576
  },
  {
    "text": "at this particular time.",
    "start": 820.88,
    "duration": 1.816
  },
  {
    "text": "And if we are going to have",
    "start": 822.72,
    "duration": 2.536
  },
  {
    "text": "over 350 trillion dollars",
    "start": 825.28,
    "duration": 4.256
  },
  {
    "text": "by 2030,",
    "start": 829.56,
    "duration": 1.536
  },
  {
    "text": "those dollars need to be\nin the hands of women.",
    "start": 831.12,
    "duration": 3.256
  },
  {
    "text": "And so I grew up with isirika.",
    "start": 834.4,
    "duration": 3.816
  },
  {
    "text": "My mother was isirika.",
    "start": 838.24,
    "duration": 1.736
  },
  {
    "text": "She was not a project or a program.",
    "start": 840.0,
    "duration": 2.08
  },
  {
    "text": "And now, I pass that to you.",
    "start": 843.24,
    "duration": 2.696
  },
  {
    "text": "That you will be able\nto share this with your families,",
    "start": 845.96,
    "duration": 3.136
  },
  {
    "text": "with your friends",
    "start": 849.12,
    "duration": 1.456
  },
  {
    "text": "and with your community,",
    "start": 850.6,
    "duration": 1.776
  },
  {
    "text": "and embrace isirika as a way of living --",
    "start": 852.4,
    "duration": 4.496
  },
  {
    "text": "as a pragmatic way of living.",
    "start": 856.92,
    "duration": 2.296
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 859.24,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 860.48,
    "duration": 1.776
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 862.28,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 863.52,
    "duration": 1.256
  },
  {
    "text": "Thank you.",
    "start": 864.8,
    "duration": 1.216
  },
  {
    "text": "(Applause)",
    "start": 866.04,
    "duration": 2.6
  }
]